4. **Unit test: DisplayController.buildStatusLine with displayName** (this is private, test indirectly via `updateStatusLine` or extract to testable helper)
   - Main session with displayName shows title instead of 'MAIN'
   - Main session without displayName shows 'MAIN'

5. **Integration test: createOnLineHandler with onTitleUpdate** (extend `tests/claude/watch-builder.test.ts`)
   - custom-title line on MAIN label triggers `onTitleUpdate` callback
   - custom-title line on subagent label does NOT trigger `onTitleUpdate`

